frames.caption: In a dark, dense forest, a grand piano is engulfed in bright flames, casting an eerie glow. The surrounding trees stand tall under a stormy sky, with flashes of lightning illuminating the scene.
frames.description: The scene is set in a mysterious forest at night, where a grand piano is dramatically on fire. The contrast between the dark trees and the bright flames creates a striking visual effect, enhanced by the stormy atmosphere.

frames.caption: A grand piano is engulfed in flames in the middle of a dark, dense forest. The fiery blaze contrasts sharply with the shadowy silhouettes of towering trees surrounding the scene. The sky above is overcast, adding to the dramatic and mysterious atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set in a dark forest, where a grand piano is burning intensely. The surrounding trees create a sense of isolation and mystery, while the flames provide the only source of light, casting an eerie glow.
